      <strong>FRIGORÍFICOS BLE SAS</strong> realiza sobre los datos personales.
    </p>
    <p>
      ·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Presentar solicitudes y reclamos
